---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Pensteady" description="Learn about Pensteady's mission to help businesses grow through steady, high-quality SEO content.">
  <Navigation />
  
  <main>
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-navy mb-8 text-center">About Pensteady</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Pensteady was built on a simple observation: most businesses know they need to publish content for SEO, but they struggle to do it consistently.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mt-12 mb-6">The Problem</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Content marketing is time-consuming. Between keyword research, writing, editing, and publishing, a single blog post can take hours. Small businesses and startups often start strong but lose momentum after a few months.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The result? Inconsistent publishing, missed SEO opportunities, and stagnant organic traffic.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mt-12 mb-6">Our Solution</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Pensteady takes the entire content workflow off your plate. We handle keyword research, content creation, SEO optimization, and publishing—all on a predictable monthly schedule.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          You get professional, SEO-optimized blog content delivered consistently, without the time commitment or hiring headaches.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mt-12 mb-6">Our Approach</h2>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 mb-8">
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-navy">No AI hype</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">We use AI as a tool, not a gimmick. Every article is reviewed and optimized by real humans.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-navy">SEO-first</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">Every article is built around target keywords with proper on-page optimization.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-navy">Consistent quality</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">Same high standard every month. No surprises, no off-brand content.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-navy">Full transparency</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">You see everything—keyword reports, content calendars, and performance metrics.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mt-12 mb-6">Why "Pensteady"?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The name reflects our philosophy: steady, reliable content beats sporadic bursts every time. SEO rewards consistency. Rankings compound. Traffic grows.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We're not here to promise overnight results or viral hits. We're here to help you build a content foundation that drives steady, predictable growth.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-amber/10 border-l-4 border-amber rounded-lg p-6 mt-12">
          <p class="text-lg text-navy font-medium mb-2">Ready to grow steadily?</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Let's talk about your content goals.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-amber text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-amber/90 transition-colors">
            Get Started
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
